      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1666.6666587,
          "startTime": 2.4666666587
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1800,
          "startTime": 2.6
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4300,
          "startTime": 5.1
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7433.333333299999,
          "startTime": 8.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、mihoさん。お誕生日おめでとうございます\n甘酒、お好きだと聞いたので、これ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4299.999610600001,
          "startTime": 11.8999996106
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "……あら、ありがとう。わざわざ私にまで\n誕生日プレゼントを用意するなんて、律儀なことね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "そういうmihoさんも、私にプレゼントしてくれた\nじゃないですか。ハンドクリーム、愛用してます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9894328434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのしきたりのようだから、渡しただけよ\n買いだめしておいた物の余りだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.8227661768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "む……それでも、私は嬉しかったんです\nあ、公式チャンネルの動画も、凄く面白かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "直近だと……franが背景を合成して妙なことをする\nシュールな動画ね。というか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "……いくら嫌いでも、さすがにもう、家族の前で\n故人を貶めたりしないわ。悪かったと思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8949631034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "（この間ああ言ってから、前より絡んでくるように）\n（なったわね。……馴れ合うつもりはないのだけれど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "あとは、年末のカウントダウンライブも最高でした\n衣装も新曲も華やかで、とってもお正月っぽくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、個人的には『Friend Glass』も\n聴きたかったですけどね。あの曲、気に入ってて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "既存の曲より、新曲の方が話題になるでしょう\nまぁ……確かにあの曲も、年末年始に似合うけれど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "友情や未来について歌っているし、それこそ新たな未来\n――新年を控えた年末に似合うと思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、年末の国民的な歌番組で歌う……とか\nさぞ似合ったことでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私もそう思いますけど……なんだかトゲが……\nもしかして、その番組のことで何かあったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "別に。嫌なことを思い出しただけよ。貴方の姉と\n何があろうと、貴方には関係ないわ。忘れなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "（えぇぇ……お姉ちゃんと何があったんだろう……）\n（でも、少しだけ、私のことは認めてくれてるのかな？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ……これからもあの曲は歌い続けるわ\nⅢXとして。どんな場所でも、どんな形でもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.5956062313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "出る時間だから、行くわ。あぁ……それとリーダーなら\nメンバーのセンスについて、少しは気にしておくことね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.3666575114,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7366.675821900003,
          "startTime": 171.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "……？　センスって……ま、待って下さいmihoさん\nまさか沙季と何かあったんですか？　mihoさーん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}